Layer.Name: landwatermask
Layer.Title: 1 Million Scale - Land/Water Mask 100 Meter Resolution
Layer.Abstract: This Land/Water Mask is a 100-meter resolution image of the conterminous United States, Alaska, Hawaii, Puerto Rico and the U.S. Virgin Islands, with separate values for oceans and for land areas of the United States, Canada, Mexico, the Bahamas and Cuba, Russia, and the British Virgin Islands.

Layer.Name: naturalearth
Layer.Title: 1 Million Scale - Natural Earth Shaded Relief 100 Meter Resolution
Layer.Abstract: This map layer contains a natural-earth image of the conterminous United States, Alaska, Hawaii, Puerto Rico and the U.S. Virgin Islands. The image is land cover in natural colors combined with shaded relief, which produces a naturalistic rendition of the Earth's surface.
